  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut milk and whole milk in a saucepan over medium heat until barely simmering.",
    "Whisk in the agar-agar powder until fully dissolved.",
    "Add minced garlic, sea salt, black pepper, and maple syrup; stir until fragrant, about 2 minutes.",
    "Stir in vanilla extract and a drop of liquid smoke, then remove from heat.",
    "Fold in the smoked tofu cubes, ensuring even coating.",
    "Pour the mixture into small ramekins or glass cups.",
    "Chill in the refrigerator for at least 60 minutes until set and aerated.",
    "Serve chilled, garnished with a sprinkle of smoked paprika or fresh herbs."
